  <summary date="2019-11-01T13:35:09Z" status="Introduced in House">Family Savings for Kids and Seniors Act

This bill increases the amount that employees may exclude from their gross income for employer-provided dependent care assistance. The bill increases the existing $5,000 limit by requiring annual adjustments that account for inflation.</summary>
